data.description: Imagine waking up to the breathtaking mountain peaks or relaxing on your front porch watching the city light up as the sun sets.  This lot offers the best of both worlds, with panoramic views that create the perfect setting to frame your dream home.  Surrounded by exquisite homes in a highly sought-after neighborhood, this lot is .4 acres, and with generous space between properties, you can create a private and secluded oasis on one of the few remaining lots in the area.  North Ogden is a haven for outdoor enthusiasts, to explore nearby trails, embark on mountain adventures, or simply soak in the natural beauty that surrounds you.  This vacant lot is more than just land; it's an opportunity to create a lifestyle that is as exceptional as the views it offers.  Adjoining lot is also available (MLS 1895060) 1032 e Nebo Avenue, North Ogden Utah 84414.  Combined the lots would give you .82 acres.
